mixin error404
  h1 404!
  h3 The page you are looking for has not been found!
  h4
    | The page you are looking for might have been removed, had its name changed, or unavailable.
    br
    | Maybe you could try a search:
  form(action='http://themepixels.com/demo/webpage/bracket/search-results.html')
    input.form-control(type='text', placeholder='Search for page')
    button.btn.btn-success Search

